d: ShowBuzzDaily's Top 150 Monday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 4.6.2020|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|date=April 7, 2020|work=Showbuzz Daily|accessdate=April 7, 2020}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = 000000\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber   = 86\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 19\n |Title           = The Sovereigns\n |RTitle          = <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/listings/20200403cbs10/|title=The Sovereigns |publisher=[[The Futon Critic]]|accessdate=April 6, 2020}}</ref>\n |DirectedBy      = [[Carlos Bernard]]\n |WrittenBy       = Pamela Wechsler\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|4|13}}\n |ProdCode        = \n |Viewers         = \n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = 000000\n}}\n}}\n\n==Ratings==\n===Season 1===\n{{Television episode ratings\n| width     = 99\n\n| title1   = [[#ep1|The Necklace]]\n| date1    = September 20, 2016\n| rs1      = 2.2/8\n| viewers1 = 15.57<ref name=\"1.01\"/>\n| dvr1     = 0.9\n| dvrv1    = 4.94\n| total1   = 3.1\n| totalv1  = 20.51<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/10/04/broadcast-live-7-ratings-sept-19-25-2016/|title='Designated Survivor' is your premiere week DVR champion: Broadcast Live +7 ratings|last=Porter|first=Rick|date=October 4, 2016|work=TV by the Numbers|accessdate=October 4, 2016}}</ref>\n\n| title2   = [[#ep2|The Woman in 8D]]\n| date2    = September 27, 2016\n| rs2      = 1.9/7\n| viewers2 = 13.62<ref name=\"1.02\"/>\n| dvr2     = 1.0\n| dvrv2    = 4.86\n| total2   = 2.9\n| totalv2  = 18.48<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/dvr-ratings/broadcast-live-7-ratings-sept-26-oct-2-2016/|title='Designated Survivor' posts more big DVR gains: Broadcast Live +7 ratings for Sept. 26-Oct. 2|last=Porter|first=Rick|date=October 11, 2016|work=TV by the Numbers|accessdate=October 11, 2016}}</ref>\n\n| title3   = [[#ep3|Unambiguous]]\n| date3    = October 11, 2016\n| rs3      = 1.7/6\n| viewers3 = 13.00<ref name=\"1.03\"/>\n| dvr3     = 0.8\n| dvrv3    = 4.