 2019}}</ref>\n\n{{Aired episodes|2020|4|6|showpage=Bull (2016 TV series)|title=Bull|finished=}}\n\n==Series overview==\n<onlyinclude>{{Series overview\n| infoA      = Rank\n| infoB      = Average viewership<br />(in millions)\n\n| color1     = #FF6229\n| link1      = <includeonly>List of Bull episodes</includeonly>#Season 1 (2016\u201317)\n| episodes1  = 23\n| start1     = {{Start date|2016|9|20}}\n| end1       = {{End date|2017|5|23}}\n| infoA1     = 5\n| infoB1     = 15.21<ref name=\"2016-2017AvgRatings\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/05/2016-2017-tv-season-ratings-series-rankings-list-1202102340/|title=Final 2016\u201317 TV Rankings: 'Sunday Night Football' Winning Streak Continues|website=Deadline Hollywood|last=de Moraes|first=Lisa|date=May 26, 2017|accessdate=May 26, 2017|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6qv7Uhg4R?url=http://deadline.com/2017/05/2016-2017-tv-season-ratings-series-rankings-list-1202102340/|archivedate=June 2, 2017|url-status=live|df=}}</ref>\n\n| color2     = #284194\n| link2      = <includeonly>List of Bull episodes</includeonly>#Season 2 (2017\u201318)\n| episodes2  = 22\n| start2     = {{Start date|2017|9|26}}\n| end2       = {{End date|2018|5|8}}\n| infoA2     = 8\n| infoB2     = 14.37<ref name=\"2017-2018AvgRatings\">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/05/2017-2018-tv-series-ratings-rankings-full-list-of-shows-1202395851/|title=2017-18 TV Series Ratings Rankings: NFL Football, 'Big Bang' Top Charts|website=Deadline Hollywood|last=de Moraes|first=Lisa|date=May 22, 2018|accessdate=May 22, 2018}}</ref>\n\n| color3     = #D7812B\n| link3      = <includeonly>List of Bull episodes</includeonly>#Season 3 (2018\u201319)\n| episodes3  = 22\n| start3     = {{Start date|2018|9|24}}\n| end3       = {{End date|2019|5|13}}\n| infoA3     = 16\n| infoB3     = 11.36<ref name=Variety>{{cite news |url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/most-watched-tv-shows-highest-rated-2018-2019-season-game-of-thrones-1203222287/ |title=100 Most-Watche